            "title": "Atour Lifestyle Holdings cuts dividend by 6.7% to $0.42/ADS, $400M buyback",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Atour Lifestyle Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ATAT\" title=\"Atour Lifestyle Holdings Limited\">ATAT</a></span>) declares <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20113085-atour-lifestyle-holdings-limited-announces-dividend-and-share-repurchase-program\">$0.42/ADS annual dividend</a>, <font color=\"red\">-6.7% decrease</font> from prior dividend of $0.45.</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ATAT/dividends/yield?source=news_bullet\">Forward yield</a> 1.39%</li>\n<li>Payable June 18; for shareholders of record June 18; ex-div June 18.</li>\n<li>The Board adopted the Annual Dividend Policy in August 2024, under which the Company plans to declare and distribute dividends with an aggregate amount of no less than 50% of its net income for the preceding financial year in each of the three financial years commencing in 2024.</li>\n<li>The board also authorized a three-year share repurchase program of up to US$400 million</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ATAT/dividends?source=news_bullet\">See ATAT Dividend Scorecard, Yield Chart, &amp; Dividend Growth.</a></li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
